&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced and enthusiastic part time Practice Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have 10,500 patients and are a dynamic, forward thinking and innovative GP training practice using EMIS web clinical system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are based in the beautiful market town of Great Dunmow which has fantastic transport links. Our team are very supportive and keen to facilitate training and staff development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our nursing team provide specialised respiratory and diabetes clinics, cytology, travel, contraception, childhood immunisations and wound management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The salary is negotiable and competitive according to skills and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is also being advertised on the Essex Primary Care Careers website – pleasecomplete only one application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have the right to close the advert earlier if we reach the maximum number of applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NO AGENCIES PLEASE&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Candidate&lt;/strong&gt;If you are an experienced Practice Nurse looking for an exciting new change in career then we would love to hear from you. You will have the following skills and qualifications:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A relevant nursing degree and experience in a General Practice setting;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current NMC registration with an active PIN;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fundamentals of Practice Nursing course (General Practice Nurse Foundation Programme) or equivalent experience or qualifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The applicant must be experienced and enthusiastic, preferably with chronic disease management skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Angel Lane Surgery are a friendly innovative dispensing practice using EMIS Web clinical system with 10500 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
